paragraphs.text:
%sql
SELECT rf.*, lr.*
FROM (
select round(incentive, 4) AS incentive, avg(prob_p) AS rf_prob_p, avg(prob_3) AS rf_prob_3, avg(actual_p) AS rf_actual_p, avg(actual_3) AS rf_actual_3
from rf_pred 
GROUP BY round(incentive, 4)
) rf
LEFT OUTER JOIN (
select round(incentive, 4) AS incentive, avg(prob_p) AS lr_prob_p, avg(prob_3) AS lr_prob_3, avg(actual_p) AS lr_actual_p, avg(actual_3) AS lr_actual_3
from lr_pred 
GROUP BY round(incentive, 4)
) lr ON lr.incentive = rf.incentive
ORDER BY rf.incentive
